{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_10", "eventName": "破碎日冕", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "10-6", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "雖非同族", "storyInfo": "費斯特帶領阿米婭等人來到自救軍地下據點，眾人結識自救軍指揮官克洛維希婭。蔓德拉向薩卡茲請罪，與曼弗雷德再次達成合作。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......回到倫蒂尼姆的第一百八十六天。"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又有三名士兵加入了我們。兩名受傷很重。只有羅本還能戰鬥。"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只在這一個區，就至少還有七十名士兵被困在敵人手裡。"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "整個倫蒂尼姆都已淪陷。被俘士兵數量無法估計。"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道他們是不是還活著。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我更不知道是否該慶幸他們還活著。"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每天都有好不容易活下來的人永遠離開。我想記住他們每一個人的名字，但事實上，很多士兵在見到我的時候，甚至已經無法開口。"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我多希望能多一個人聽聽他們的聲音。我多麼希望......能有一個人在身邊聽聽我的聲音。"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但願你有一天能看到這些記錄。"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但願你在外面的任務還順利。"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但願你不要這麼快回到倫蒂尼姆......"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_warehouse", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "號角，新來的幾個士兵已經安置好了。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 麻煩你了，布萊克。暫時不要給他們安排任務，他們需要先適應兩天。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 號角，我不用適應！我隨時都能出去殺敵！", "name": "羅本"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......行。布萊克，把羅本編入四隊，正常輪班偵察。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是，號角。挺好的，最近深池又活躍了起來，我們正需要人手。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 三隊還沒回來。羅本，你最好原地休息一會。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可以做點別的......", "name": "羅本"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我建議你過來坐下。我們最多只有半個小時，別浪費。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......好。", "name": "羅本"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 還有，我理解你的心情。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 想出去對付敵人，是吧？你覺得早上那場仗還沒打夠。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，我的手還在發抖！它希望我能再多握一會弓弩！", "name": "羅本"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......羅本，記住一件事。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我們待在這裡，不是為了多消滅幾個深池士兵，或者幾個薩卡茲。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我們的首要目的是活著。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 然後是......讓更多我們的人也能活下來。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#6$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "號角......我......", "name": "羅本"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白了。", "name": "羅本"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 明白就好。抓緊休息吧。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#6$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......您手裡的這是？", "name": "羅本"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 備忘錄。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#6$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 只是隨手寫寫，不用太在意。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#6$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我記得您說過，您有很長時間都是一個人行動。", "name": "羅本"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難怪您會有這個習慣......", "name": "羅本"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 哈哈......或許是做別人的隊長做久了吧。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#6$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 沒人聽我說話，總像是缺了點什麼。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 也多虧了布萊克他們從深池手裡搶了這支筆，要不然我真是只能用小刀在下水管道上刻字了。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您真的這麼做過嗎？", "name": "羅本"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 去最外面的排水層找找，你說不定能看到我親手刻下的《維多利亞，一段歷史》。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#6$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那......得刻上多久啊？", "name": "羅本"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......我開玩笑的。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#6$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 閒聊留給以後吧，深池的士兵隨時可能回到附近。我閉會眼，你也是。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#6$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g4_giantwall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "將軍，深池的那個菲林術師來了，她說她想見你。", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她一個人？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，她沒有帶其他手下。", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓她上來。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "將軍，她的源石技藝很難防備......", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在你眼裡，我連這種層次的源石技藝都對付不了嗎？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#8$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我絕對不會這麼想！將軍，你和特雷西斯將軍一樣，都是我最佩服的戰士！", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就去你該去的地方。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#8$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是！", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫德雷，你留下。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在見過赦罪師的信使之後，你應該有了心理準備。有一項工作需要交給你。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想讓我把從那艘船上來的人找出來？", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你曾與他們共事過。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_393_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是雇傭兵。雇傭兵從來不會特意記住共事過的每一個人，除非他的腦袋特別值錢。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#4$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對付熟人，總會容易些，不是嗎？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......也許。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那名巴別塔的刺客已經身在中央城區。防備她是赦罪師們的任務。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#3$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於其他人......赫德雷，你猜猜他們都有誰？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_393_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "城內的雇傭兵還未發現他們之中任何一個的蹤跡。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#7$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們遲早會有所行動。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這半年以來，我們在維多利亞的眼線一直追蹤著那艘船的位置。但他們卻總能快我們一步，甚至能不被察覺地靠近倫蒂尼姆。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你覺得這是什麼原因？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_393_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只有一種可能性。他們在倫蒂尼姆有暗樁。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#6$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "暗樁......是啊，暗樁。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#4$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樁子恐怕在很多年前就已經插下，而且根基不淺。否則的話，一定很難逃過我們的眼睛。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#7$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......很合理。在我印象中，那位勳爵......那位醫生的手段難以估量。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫德雷，把最近我們抓到的反抗者的底細都再仔細查一查。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你懷疑我們已經抓到了人？", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果羅德島的人還在附近逗留，他們一定有不得不這麼做的理由。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g7_subway", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$bar_intro", "key": "$bar_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "1:15 P.M. 天氣/陰"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倫蒂尼姆，薩迪恩區，地下結構"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們到了。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_403_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼人？！", "name": "戰士比爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_403_1#1$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老比爾，是我，我回來了。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_403_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來是你小子。我剛看到洛洛了，你們不是一起出任務了嗎？", "name": "戰士比爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_403_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，她有事先回來。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_403_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你帶的這些人......等等，薩卡茲？！", "name": "戰士比爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_403_1#1$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_bldwhoosh", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別別別動手——", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#11$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們很可能就是指揮官在等的人！", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_403_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......指揮官在等的難道不是幫手？既然是幫手，怎麼會是一堆魔族！", "name": "戰士比爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_403_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老比爾，你饒了我吧。指揮官在哪裡？我馬上去見她。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#3$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_403_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "戰士比爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_403_1#1$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行行好。你覺得我有一絲當叛徒的可能性嗎？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#3$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_403_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這倒沒有。這裡每個人都把你當家裡的兄弟。", "name": "戰士比爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_403_1#1$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "洛洛讓你守在這，沒錯吧？你多叫幾個人，帶著我們一起去。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_403_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......行，聽你的。", "name": "戰士比爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_403_1#1$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_403_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於你們，別想輕舉妄動。我們會盯著你們的，薩卡茲。", "name": "戰士比爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_403_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_411_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃......阿米婭，我們好像前所未有地不受歡迎。", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#6$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_411_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我也感覺到了。;......; 這合作有些艱難。", "values": "1;2;3"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line225", "option2": "line225", "option3": "line225"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2;3"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對不起了。大家平時不是這樣子的，只是對你們中某幾位的......樣貌有些神經過敏。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等指揮官發話，肯定會好很多。跟我來吧，他們就在前面開會。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#9$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g6_hideout", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "channel": "slide", "loop": "true", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們都沒聽見嗎？他們用城防炮轟炸了出入口！我們不能再繼續留在這裡！風險太大了！", "name": "憤怒的青年男聲"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可要是離開薩迪恩區，我們就很難再回來救人了。", "name": "平靜的中年女聲"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也想救他們。你以為我不想嗎？但你知道我們的人被關在哪裡？難道要我們的戰士走到薩卡茲面前一間屋子一間屋子找過去嗎？", "name": "憤怒的青年男聲"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費斯特和洛洛他們一直在打探消息。", "name": "平靜的中年女聲"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太慢了！情況有變，我們好不容易建起來的根據地，隨時都可能被薩卡茲轟成散沙！", "name": "憤怒的青年男聲"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "基地是死的，人是活的。", "name": "平靜的中年女聲"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說得輕巧！反正一點點地把這地方建起來的人不是你們這些做生意的！", "name": "憤怒的青年男聲"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "他們似乎正在爭吵。;我們來得是時候嗎？", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line253", "option2": "line256"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line259"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，是有些小爭執。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "2"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line259"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係，指揮官不會介意。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": true}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們隊伍裡的人出身差別很大，有時候意見不統一，但大家的心是齊的。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且再怎麼吵，只要有指揮官在，最後都會有個結果。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#9$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "你們都很信任她。;她真的這麼厲害？", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line267", "option2": "line267"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔......我們中的大多數都是她救的。要不是指揮官，我們都早就死在了薩卡茲或者深池的手裡。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#4$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像洛洛，他爸爸就因為不願意出賣城防軍的情報而被幾個雇傭兵活活打死了。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#5$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的話，我也不想給薩卡茲幹活，當初帶著幾個同事一起從西邊的海布里區一路逃過來，差點餓死在接駁管道裡......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#5$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後也是指揮官發現了我們。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#5$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是她把我們一個個地從絕境裡拉出來，並且把我們聚在一起。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#5$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們都很佩服她，也相信她能帶領我們渡過一個又一個絕境。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "指揮官，你說吧，我們該不該立刻轉移？", "name": "憤怒的青年男聲"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "指揮官，我建議我們馬上展開救援行動。", "name": "平靜的中年女聲"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "指揮官......", "name": "其他七八個聲音"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "slide", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈默，泰勒，你們都冷靜一些。", "name": "年輕的聲音"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "時間緊迫，爭執無益。", "name": "年輕的聲音"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個聲音......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#8$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜，你怎麼了？", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#5$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，沒什麼，大概是我的錯覺。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 費斯特先生，最後說話的人是你們的指揮官嗎？她聽起來......年紀很小。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很意外是不是？我剛認識指揮官的時候，和你發出了一模一樣的感慨。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#7$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記得剛才嗎，卡特斯小姐，我第一眼看到你，就認出了你是領隊的那個。你很快就會知道這是為什麼了。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來吧，見見我們的指揮官。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "27_i03", "fadetime": 0.5, "xScale": 0.9, "yScale": 0.9}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "27_i03", "xScaleTo": 1.1, "yScaleTo": 1.1, "duration": 50.0}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諸位，你們各自的心情我都很理解。但是，有一點是不需要討論的。", "name": "年輕的聲音"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的人，我們一定會去救。", "name": "年輕的聲音"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倘若我們任由敵人傷害我們的戰士，之後還有誰會願意與我們並肩戰鬥？", "name": "年輕的聲音"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倘若我們任由敵人抓走我們的朋友，之後還有誰會願意向我們伸出援手？", "name": "年輕的聲音"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們是倫蒂尼姆市民自救軍。我們要拯救倫蒂尼姆，在這之前，我們必須救出那一個個我們熟悉的、活生生的人。", "name": "年輕的聲音"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那雙抬起的手細瘦、小巧，堪稱稚嫩。但它似乎有著足夠的力量，能夠壓住即將沸騰的憤怒與焦灼。"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "會議現場安靜了下來。"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們的目光聚集在他們的指揮官身上，如此自然，就彷彿從未有人質疑過那瘦小的肩膀能否承受住這些沉甸甸的希望。"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個畫面有些熟悉。"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "許多羅德島幹員都冒出了這個想法。他們不約而同地看向了站在他們身前的卡特斯。"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g6_hideout", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我懂費斯特的意思了。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_411_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸欸，還真有點像，對吧對吧？", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#10$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_411_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我同意。;......; 還是不一樣。", "values": "1;2;3"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line344", "option2": "line344", "option3": "line344"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2;3"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 大家......小聲些，不要打擾他們開會。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來，在討論具體的救援方案之前，我們還需要見幾位新朋友。", "name": "年輕的聲音"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費斯特，請帶他們過來吧。", "name": "年輕的聲音"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊......是，指揮官！", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們好，羅德島的各位，我一直在期待你們的到來。", "name": "年輕的聲音"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我叫克洛維希婭，倫蒂尼姆市民自救軍的指揮官。", "name": "年輕的聲音"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g4_giantwall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "將軍，深池的指揮官到了。", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......蔓德拉女士。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#2"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#2"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "曼弗雷德......將軍。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我相信你來找我，是有重要的事想與我們商談。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#2"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你......哼，你明明什麼都看見了，卻非得裝出這副樣子......", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#2"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "蔓德拉", "content": "你真的是薩卡茲嗎？別的薩卡茲都不像你這麼......"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#2"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "蔓德拉", "content": "會耍弄心思。"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蔓德拉女士，你剛才的言論，對薩卡茲來說已經算得上一種侮辱。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#9$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#2"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......隨你怎麼說。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#2"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#5"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "反正......我是來道歉的。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#5"}, {"id": 395, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦？道歉？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#2"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之前在下面的出入口，我們的人與你們之間產生了一些誤會。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#2"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......誤會。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 401, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#5"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......來這裡，就是想再確認一次......我們之間的合作依然有效。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#5"}, {"id": 403, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女士，我不妨再提醒你一次。我們並沒有什麼實質性的合作條款需要遵守。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 405, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "深池不干涉任何薩卡茲在倫蒂尼姆的行動，我們就容許你們在某一範圍內停留。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "曼弗雷德", "content": "你可以把這當作我們之間的......"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "曼弗雷德", "content": "某種默契。"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你說過的，我沒忘記。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，忘了也沒關係。之前那番小小的動靜，就當作對你的提醒吧。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#9$1"}, {"id": 415, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#5"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#5"}, {"id": 417, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感......謝。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先別急著道謝。薩卡茲從來不像你們那樣容易忘事。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 421, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#5"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你想要我怎麼做？難道你想要我的命？你們真想這麼做的話......", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#5"}, {"id": 423, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想這麼做的話，你走不到這裡。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 425, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......你甚至沒法走下幾個月前的西部大堂的臺階。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 427, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#4"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃......", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#4"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們想看見的，是深池的一點誠意。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#4$1"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，不是從我們手裡搶走維多利亞士兵，或者綁架一兩個逃脫的倫蒂尼姆市民那種“誠意”。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#4$1"}, {"id": 433, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們是時候展開一些......真正的合作了。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#5$1"}, {"id": 435, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_warehouse", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 號角！", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 447, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 怎麼了？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 449, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我不想打擾你，但薩利他......他快支撐不住了！他那條傷腿已經腫得連膿水都擠不出來了......", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 451, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 453, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 三隊回來了嗎？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 455, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 456, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 沒有，今天上午外面很亂，他們可能耽擱得有點久。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 457, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 458, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我們還有多少人手？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 459, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 460, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 加上新來的，能戰鬥的還有十七個人。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 461, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 462, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 二隊的留下，你們繼續負責警戒。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 463, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 464, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我帶五個人出去，我們再去拜訪下深池借來的住處。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 465, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 466, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 這......你又折回去的話，萬一撞上蔓德拉怎麼辦？", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 467, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 468, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......薩利等不了。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 469, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 470, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 他急需用藥。沒有鎮痛劑和消炎藥物的話，他甚至熬不過今天下午。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 471, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 472, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 你們誰身上還有值錢的東西？嗯？光是每天換來足夠的食物，都需要老艾頓絞盡腦汁了。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 473, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 474, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我們不去問深池要的話，難不成要去問薩卡茲？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 475, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 476, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 還是說......你們想去向平民伸手？如果他們出手幫了我們，敵人會怎麼對付他們，你們都想過嗎？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 477, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 478, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 唉......", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 479, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 480, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 垂頭喪氣可換不來戰友的命。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#7$1"}, {"id": 481, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 482, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 都收拾收拾，帶上能用的武器，我們立刻出發。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#7$1"}, {"id": 483, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 484, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 羅本，你不是說沒殺夠嗎？你很幸運，瞧啊，機會這麼快又來了。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 485, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 486, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 